      "Key": "64CF0107426FDA2ED0CC53B0F07F11A8",
      "SourceString": "Add to a weapon's Relic Slot while crafting to deal ELEMENTAL LIGHTNING damage and use the Electrokinesis ability. Strong against ICE. \n\nDeal more ELEMENTAL LIGHTNING Damage.\n\nElectrokinesis - Charge your weapon by dealing damage. When fully charged, use <keybind touch_img=\"Electrokinesis\">Target</> to launch yourself into the air, then use primary attack to hurl a bolt of LIGHTNING.",
